        Great for implants
        


        Posted by Unknown on 9th Mar 2017
    
I knew what I was ordering. This floss is great for all the implants I have. Great delivery, too.
Thanks Amazon for continuing to have wonderful vendors!




        Nice but, could be better
        


        Posted by Kurt Hertel on 24th Jun 2016
    
I have been using these for 11 years due to implants and bridges. My dentist recommended them and I have liked the idea of not having to use a leader loop to pass the floss under the appliance. I usually get the 10 pkg. The last batch I received seemed to be constructed of poorer quality than the previous (12 or so) batches. The blue coating used to stiffen the leader ends seemed to be less thick allowing the ends to bend with very little resistance and as a result I had to resort to the loop leader. The whole idea, for me, was to eliminate this step. After finishing the first of my 10 boxes last week I can report that the issue I've had seems to have been corrected. Perhaps I just got a poor batch. All in all a great idea and a good product.



        Tried them all!
        


        Posted by Unknown on 5th Feb 2016
    
I have a 4 post full upper implant that is difficult to clean. I have tried every product on the market. This threader/floss combo is by far the best. Please improve the packaging. Mine are in a snack bag.



        Best implant - bridge floss
        


        Posted by Unknown on 15th Mar 2015
    
This is the best and is well worth the price.



        cleanest by far
        


        Posted by Hope Eknoian on 1st Mar 2015
    
I have used these for a few years and they are great.  If ONLY they could find a better way of packing.  Pulling one out, and they all follow.  I undo the whole thing and get them all together and put a bread wrapper clip and then just have to pull one and get ONE! Takes up a lot of room, but so much easier. Also great foe cleaning hearing aids!!!! Just the right size to be tight!!!!



        Great Item
        


        Posted by Roger on 7th Jan 2015
    
I learned of these from my dentist and found they work GREAT. Now I keep a couple extra packs on hand at all times.



        BEST OF FLOSSES
        


        Posted by SIS on 14th Dec 2014
    
I mentioned to my hygienist last time there that seems the super flosses are not as thick as they used to be. She gave me a pkg. of these flosses to try. I found these are exactly what I need to get the job done right. I have several permanent bridges and some implants. So happy now!!



