Welcome to Thornton & Ross DirectFrom a base in Huddersfield, West Yorkshire, Thornton & Ross develop, manufacture and supply a wide and growing range of branded OTC medicines, dermatological preparations, niche generic medicines and other pharmaceutical, healthcare and hygiene products.  Founded in 1922, Thornton & Ross has grown to become one of the largest OTC pharmaceutical manufacturers in the UK. We continue to grow our business every year and are now selling a selection of our product range direct to consumers.Browse Our Online Products

   

   

   

          
